{"tid":1116442,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[冇圖]屋企隻貓成日食昆蟲","createTime":"2019-04-20T04:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T06:00:42.000Z","uid":205169,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"052818c862f81e87ffdabd42eb9f7ceff8650c6c","tid":1116442,"uid":205169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:06:44.000Z","msg":"之前已經成日撲d 飛黎飛去既蟬bb（唔知係咪 好嘈又好細隻）一掌拍隻野落地 之後用手撥黎撥去 玩死佢<br />\n有一日正當我想用紙巾執走條屍既時候<br />\n佢突然嗚個頭落去 個嘴𡁻𡁻下<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢已經瞬間食左落肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />阻止都黎唔切 <br />\n唔知係咪呢排落雨多左昆蟲 <br />\n連續幾日都俾佢捉到曱甴<br />\n玩到隻野反肚不特止仲想食左佢 <br />\n處理好條屍之前仲係咁想行埋黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似好鍾意食咁<br />\n想問下食咁多 會唔會有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見到都仲阻止到 好驚屋企冇人既時候佢就開餐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c555a98e6ea9e9fdca1d9e83830b357057a2d9","tid":1116442,"uid":12618,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:07:35.000Z","msg":"想食啲野味姐"},{"pid":"f7ce4cc68002d3b491b85b2ba805fbcd83d0d6b0","tid":1116442,"uid":205169,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"98c555a98e6ea9e9fdca1d9e83830b357057a2d9","tid":1116442,"uid":12618,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:07:35.000Z","msg":"想食啲野味姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:08:54.000Z","msg":"補充蛋白質？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc4e740893eb1dd832dcb2dacbbeb16